    "The spectral shape of the GWB signal, S turb (f), is",
    "where B 50 λ * H * -2 is a normalising factor, and δt fin denotes the effective duration of the turbulence.",
    "The latter can be estimated, from the numerical simulations performed in Roper Pol et al. (2022a), to be δt fin 2λ * / √ 1.5 Ω *.",
    "The function p Π (λ * f) in Eq.",
    "(23) denotes the spectrum of the anisotropic stresses."
  ],
